<br>
I'm gonna just play the damn game and let you all do your thing.  No one is going to tell ME how I'm gonna play, nor will I try enforce my views on anyone.  <br>
<br>
If you wanna powergame, feel free.  If you wanna roleplay, more power to you.  If you wanna pump out hot air and frustration faster than Oscar Meyer can pump-out weiners, go right-a-frickin-head.<br>
<br>
Shintou, by assuming everything is going down the shithole, you are mandating your own destiny.  You'll become more irate, more frustrated, you'll berate those who don't adopt your playstyle, they'll become more resistant and start fighting back.  Self-fullfilling prophecy.  <br>
<br>
Just fricking play.  Have fun.  Or get another hobby.<br>
<br>
Me-Out!<br>
