<br>
I don't have a problem with folks doing what they want and coming up with a RP reason to justify it -- so long as it actually does justify it, however unprobable the reason.<br>
<br>
Why?  I see people do things like that ALL THE TIME in RL.  People do whatever they feel like and justify it later according to their own excuses and mores.  Does it have to make sense?  Does it even USUALLY make sense?  Nope.<br>
